--- xochitla2006 <xochitla2006@...> wrote:

> Hydras:
> 
> "Welcome to our ranks Mymidon, what are your skils?"
> said the dragon 
> robot

Myrmidon regarded the dragon robot for a moment, and
then spoke, "I am a Predacon and a hunter of all that
dare oppose us. I am a multi assault warrior, and my
skills are many. I can watch from afar or pass through
enemy lines unseen. I can attack from the skies above,
from the oceans below, or crush opponants in open
combat." Myrmidon's optics brightened fiendishly as he
spoke, his clenched fist dropping to side. "The
question is, what do you have most need of?"

Preston
(Myrmidon)
